00:01:11.862 --> 00:01:15.419
Your Majesty. For generations, the Su family
has given their lives to the Mobei royal family.

00:01:15.420 --> 00:01:17.190
The old General
fought through blood and battle

00:01:17.190 --> 00:01:18.880
on the northern frontier
for more than twenty years.

00:01:18.880 --> 00:01:19.861
Yet now,

00:01:19.862 --> 00:01:21.211
his only bloodline

00:01:21.212 --> 00:01:22.920
has been killed by the first prince.

00:01:22.920 --> 00:01:24.491
The thirty thousand soldiers
of the Su Army

00:01:24.491 --> 00:01:27.400
were all forged by the old General himself,
blade by blade and spear by spear.

00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:28.760
We kneel before Your Majesty

00:01:28.760 --> 00:01:31.000
and beg leave to lay down our armor
and return to our fields.

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:32.779
Yuwen Que!

00:01:32.782 --> 00:01:34.540
I raised you into the man you are today.

00:01:34.541 --> 00:01:37.800
And yet you show such utter disregard
for ruler and father alike.

00:01:37.800 --> 00:01:39.374
Your Majesty,
please restrain your anger.

00:01:39.374 --> 00:01:41.174
If I may be so bold,
I wish to offer a suggestion.

00:01:41.175 --> 00:01:41.824
Speak!

00:01:41.825 --> 00:01:43.661
From what I have learned,

00:01:43.662 --> 00:01:45.952
the first prince has always acted
for the good of the realm.

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:47.586
As for the stabbing of General Su,

00:01:47.587 --> 00:01:49.735
it was incited
by the performer Shen Qingru.

00:01:49.736 --> 00:01:52.699
No one knows what kind of wicked sorcery
Shen Qingru used on the first prince.

00:01:52.700 --> 00:01:54.100
With just a few words,

00:01:54.101 --> 00:01:56.240
she set two great pillars of the court
against each other.

00:01:56.240 --> 00:01:57.511
Such depth of scheming,

00:01:57.512 --> 00:01:58.741
such venomous methods,

00:01:58.742 --> 00:02:00.021
are truly abhorrent.

00:02:00.022 --> 00:02:01.599
So this is her craft of sowing discord.

00:02:01.600 --> 00:02:02.861
That Shen Qingru

00:02:02.862 --> 00:02:04.274
deserves death by a thousand cuts.

00:02:04.274 --> 00:02:06.724
We beg Your Majesty to see the truth
and grant Shen Qingru death,

00:02:06.725 --> 00:02:09.021
to appease the spirit
of the old General in heaven.

00:02:09.022 --> 00:02:10.181
Very well.

00:02:10.825 --> 00:02:12.016
Issue the order.

00:02:12.017 --> 00:02:13.656
Execute the rebel at once,

00:02:13.657 --> 00:02:15.337
Shen Qingru.

00:02:15.338 --> 00:02:17.017
Your Majesty is wise.

00:02:17.018 --> 00:02:19.327
Long live our Emperor.

00:02:21.458 --> 00:02:22.777
By the Mandate of Heaven,

00:02:22.778 --> 00:02:24.177
the Emperor decrees.

00:02:24.178 --> 00:02:26.136
Shen Qingru sowed discord,

00:02:26.137 --> 00:02:27.696
causing a meritorious official's death.

00:02:27.697 --> 00:02:29.199
Her crimes warrant execution.

00:02:29.200 --> 00:02:30.536
She is to be beheaded today

00:02:30.537 --> 00:02:32.057
to restore order to the court.

00:02:32.058 --> 00:02:34.327
So decreed.

00:02:38.458 --> 00:02:40.218
Who dares touch her?

00:02:47.858 --> 00:02:51.297
I order you, as the first prince,

00:02:51.298 --> 00:02:53.498
