00:02:54.097 --> 00:02:57.096
Your Highness, I only act on orders.

00:02:57.097 --> 00:02:59.436
Please do not put me
in a difficult position.

00:02:59.437 --> 00:03:01.392
Anyone who touches my woman

00:03:01.977 --> 00:03:04.840
will pay with his life today.

00:03:06.778 --> 00:03:08.218
Your Highness, you must not.

00:03:08.257 --> 00:03:09.974
Forcing this now will only doom her.

00:03:09.975 --> 00:03:10.976
Endure it for the moment.

00:03:10.977 --> 00:03:13.897
When His Majesty's anger subsides,
we will find another chance to save her.

00:03:17.618 --> 00:03:18.778
Take her away.

00:03:19.657 --> 00:03:20.777
