00:07:05.217 --> 00:07:07.897
Young lady, look,
that sugar figurine stall is still there.

00:07:07.898 --> 00:07:10.297
I remember you loved
osmanthus sugar figurines the most.

00:07:19.057 --> 00:07:20.617
I want to buy her freedom.

00:07:21.458 --> 00:07:22.658
Ten taels.

00:07:23.617 --> 00:07:25.057
Here is twenty taels.

00:07:25.225 --> 00:07:26.296
Deal.

00:07:26.297 --> 00:07:28.090
See to her injuries as well.

00:07:28.737 --> 00:07:29.937
Young lady.

00:07:30.018 --> 00:07:32.177
If you had not saved me back then...

00:07:35.578 --> 00:07:36.778
Take it.

00:07:36.977 --> 00:07:38.297
Thank you.

00:07:51.338 --> 00:07:52.578
Young lady.

00:07:54.657 --> 00:07:56.257
I once believed

00:07:56.818 --> 00:07:59.578
