to slaughter my entire family.

00:11:07.297 --> 00:11:08.816
What is there left to explain?

00:11:08.817 --> 00:11:09.611
It was not so.

00:11:09.612 --> 00:11:10.736
Your mother was called a boat courtesan,

00:11:10.737 --> 00:11:12.840
but in truth, she was a favored consort
of the Emperor of Cangzhou.

00:11:12.840 --> 00:11:13.696
Prince Yuwen Que

00:11:13.697 --> 00:11:15.536
was not your mother's true enemy.

00:11:15.537 --> 00:11:16.915
Impossible.

00:11:17.218 --> 00:11:18.656
But I saw him with my own eyes...

00:11:18.657 --> 00:11:20.257
Your mother was framed back then,

00:11:20.258 --> 00:11:21.627
